body.description: The Honeywell 18 inch dishwasher is compact in size allowing for more cabinet space in the kitchen. The racks are suitable to fit 8 place settings of dishes. There are 6 washing programs to choose from- heavy, normal, eco, glass, rapid, and rinse. The tub is made of stainless steel for better efficiency performance. This uses low energy consumption according to Energy Star standards. There is up to 24 hour delay start for you added convenience. The unit dimensions are 18x22.6x32.4 inches. This has UL and Energy Star certification.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 11, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Solid Dishwasher for the Price
reviews.reviewText: When I bought this dishwasher, there were not many reviews on it. I took the risk by buying it regardless and I am satisfied with my purchase. The setup was not too difficult coming from someone who’s never done something like this before. I even found a few useful installation videos from Honeywell’s YouTube channel.I would like to note that your experience with this dishwasher might vary depending on what dishwasher cycle you run, detergent you use, and how dirty the dishes are. This dishwasher does clean really well, but I’ve found that on certain dishes that have been dirty for several days, this dishwasher will not completely clean them and you might need to clean by hand.All in all, if you need an 18 inch dishwasher, you can’t go wrong with this one for the price.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 7, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Great, quiet dishwasher with some quirks
reviews.reviewText: We have a small kitchen so when we did the remodel we wanted to size down the dishwasher to fit in a full sized sink base. We did a lot of research and decided on this unit. It's incredibly short. We had to raise it all the way up to have it reach the appropriate height and my husband had to carefully place the toe kick to hide the amount of space between the bottom of the dishwasher and the floor. It runs incredibly quiet, we can't hear it at all unless we are in the kitchen, and the rapid cycle does a great job. However, it's been installed since July and the motherboard just went out on it--less than a year. Honeywell is sending a replacement unit which is appreciated but still a pain in the neck and extra work for my husband to remove and install. Hopefully the new unit lasts longer than this one did.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 23, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Looks great, cleans well
reviews.reviewText: I was reluctant to order a dishwasher from Amazon due to the fact that i imagine it is a hassle to return a bulky item like that if it would be damaged in shipping. I am really glad that i did, the unit arrived in perfect condition, no dents or anything like that. So shipping, not a problem.Appearance and dimensions, the description and the pictures are accurate, it looks great in the kitchen.It cleans the dishes well, even when i did not rinse the dishes before loading the dishwasher, just to see how it will do.I have only just had it installed so i cannot comment on how well it will do long term, but so far i do recommend this dishwasher, due to its appearance and how well it cleans, not to mention the price, it was actually cheaper than most other 18 inch dishwashers, so if you are like me and are worried about ordering an appliance on Amazon, i tried it and it was a completely positive experience for me.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great and very quiet!
reviews.reviewText: I’m not one to write reviews but I will say when I ordered this I was pretty apprehensive because of the current reviews. However, I am glad I did! This dishwasher arrived on time with no damage (I order from Amazon and not a reseller). I read that this product didn’t come with directions, mine did along with mounting brackets and hardware.This dishwasher came with the drain hose preattached but you will need to buy an install kit for the power and water supply.Lastly, this dishwasher does have a learning curve with the settings and getting everything correct. Aside from that, it has been as advertised and is extremely quiet.
